MRL.AdditionalRegulationNotes: Fresh or frozen vegetables. MRL applies to whole product. Other products to which the EU Beans (with pods) MRL applies are Azuki beans, Black eyed peas/cowpeas, Broad beans/fava beans/horse beans/tic beans, Borlotti beans/cannelini beans/common beans/flageolets/French beans/slicing beans/snap beans, Ervils/lentil vetches, Guar beans, Jack beans, Lablab beans/hyacinth beans, Lima beans/butter beans, Monantha vetches, Mung beans, Rice beans, Runner beans/scarlet runner beans, Soyabeans/edamame, Stink beans, Vetches, and Yardlong beans as designated in Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 396/2005.

Fresh or frozen vegetables. MRL applies to whole product. Other products to which the EU Beans (without pods) MRL applies are species listed with code numbers 0260010-xxx, without pods (Azuki beans, Black eyed peas/cowpeas, Broad beans/fava beans/horse beans/tic beans, Borlotti beans/cannelini beans/common beans/flageolets/French beans/slicing beans/snap beans, Ervils/lentil vetches, Guar beans, Jack beans, Lablab beans/hyacinth beans, Lima beans/butter beans, Monantha vetches, Mung beans, Rice beans, Runner beans/scarlet runner beans, Soyabeans/edamame, Stink beans, Vetches, and Yardlong beans) as designated in Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 396/2005.

MRL applies to dry seeds. Other products to which the EU Beans MRL applies are species listed with code numbers 0260010-xxx, dried seeds, except soyabeans/edamame (Azuki beans, Black eyed peas/cowpeas, Broad beans/fava beans/horse beans/tic beans, Borlotti beans/cannelini beans/common beans/flageolets/French beans/slicing beans/snap beans, Ervils/lentil vetches, Guar beans, Jack beans, Lablab beans/hyacinth beans, Lima beans/butter beans, Monantha vetches, Mung beans, Rice beans, Runner beans/scarlet runner beans, Stink beans, Vetches, and Yardlong beans) as designated in Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 396/2005.
